Title: Renames the Kingston Avenue train station to the Chabad Lubavitch World Headquarters at Kingston Avenue station
Summary: Directs the metropolitan transportation authority to rename the Kingston Avenue train station, located in the borough of Brooklyn, to the Chabad Lubavitch World Headquarters at Kingston Avenue station.
ActClause: AN ACT directing the metropolitan transportation authority to rename the Kingston Avenue train station to the Chabad Lubavitch World Headquarters at the Kingston Avenue station
